{"tid":2289882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(細膽唔好睇)（中字）絕對陰謀論紀錄片   講侵侵","createTime":"2020-11-17T14:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T14:37:56.000Z","uid":324569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8550f35908b542180bf9a2a9550a25de3f0a58","tid":2289882,"uid":324569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">好得人驚，無辦法fack check，細膽唔好睇！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">純粹八卦分享</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"navy\">The documentary is in English with Chinese subtitle. 這部紀錄片一定要看，看完就知道為什麼Google 開始查不到我們以前看過的資料？<br />\n為什麼說真話的YouTuber 、良心媒體會拿黃標白做工，甚至影片被下架。<br />\n為什麼FB、Twitter 開始白色恐佈、言論審查？<br />\n<br />\n為什麼美國、甚至全人類已經到了存亡危機？答案通通在影片裡。<br />\n<br />\n這絕對不是陰謀論，是確確實實發生的事，人們能自救的方法就是把真相擴散出去，喚醒更多人。</span><br />\n<br />\n第一集 <a href=\"https://parler.com/post/3017341b4bc44e91ad1bb1ec3aa68baf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fparler.com%2Fpost%2F3017341b4bc44e91ad1bb1ec3aa68baf&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM48ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=395f81c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://parler.com/post/3017341b4bc44e91ad1bb1ec3aa68baf</a><br />\n<br />\n第二集 <a href=\"https://parler.com/post/9aa7fd685af84c0486cfe4a5f7ff37b0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fparler.com%2Fpost%2F9aa7fd685af84c0486cfe4a5f7ff37b0&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM48ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=88da9452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://parler.com/post/9aa7fd685af84c0486cfe4a5f7ff37b0</a><br />\n<br />\n第三集 <a href=\"https://parler.com/post/0484223afc8345d1a935afd46b4c34c2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fparler.com%2Fpost%2F0484223afc8345d1a935afd46b4c34c2&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM48ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=17a82f1d\" data-auto-link target